Simpliest and easiest way to send a packet thru local or any network.
Open up scapy and make sure to indicate IP destination 
send(IP(src="IP DESTINATION xxx.xxx.x.x",dst="IP DESTINATION xxx.xxx.x.x")/ICMP()/"The world is yours")
Run code thru scapy
Open up wireshark and scan the network indicated above to see indicated words displayed 
